<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="PN226-intro">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. cōḻaṉ kuḷamuṟṟattut tuñciya kiḷḷivaḷavaṉai māṟōkkattu nappacalaiyār pāṭiyatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg style="pūṭṭuvil" xml:id="PN226">
<l>ceṟṟaṉ ṟāyiṉuñ ceyirttaṉ ṟāyiṉu</l>
<l>muṟṟaṉ ṟāyiṉu muyviṉṟu mātō</l>
<l>pāṭunar pōlak kaitoḻu tētti</l>
<l>yiṟantaṉ ṟākal vēṇṭum polantār</l>
<l>maṇṭamar kaṭakkun tāṉait</l>
<l>tiṇṭēr vaḷavaṟ koṇṭa kūṟṟē.</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="1">  Even though it destroyed, even though it raged, </l>
<l corresp="2">  even though it had [him], is it really without escape? </l>
<l corresp="6">  – Death, that took Vaḷavaṉ with firm chariot </l>
<l corresp="5">  an army that was victorious in close battle, </l>
<l corresp="4">  [and] with a golden garland who wanted it to pass by, </l>
<l corresp="3">  praising with hands folded like the singers [do]. </l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
